panels.title: Total CO2 based on estimated daily views
Total CO2 based on estimated daily views

targets.query: SELECT last("value") FROM "co2PerPageView" WHERE ("group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "category" =~ /^$category$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "origin" = 'sustainable') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("value") FROM "default"."contentSize" WHERE ("category" =~ /^$category$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "contentType" = 'css' AND "party" = 'thirdParty') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("value") FROM "default"."contentSize" WHERE ("category" =~ /^$category$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND "page" =~ /^$page$/ AND "browser" =~ /^$browser$/ AND "connectivity" =~ /^$connectivity$/ AND "contentType" = 'font' AND "party" = 'thirdParty') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT last("p90") FROM "autogen"."co2PerPageView" WHERE ("page" =~ /.*/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "page"::tag ORDER BY time DESC
